## Filtering

This data source supports filtering using the following attributes:

- `filter_type` (Required): Type of filter to apply. Valid values are `tenant_id`, `domain_name`.
- `filter_value` (Required): Value to filter by. Should be a valid tenant ID (GUID) when filter_type is 'tenant_id', or a valid domain name when filter_type is 'domain_name'.

